      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. While there are minor signs of regular use, the interior is clean and all major systems are functioning as they should. It offers a great balance of performance and dependability for its next owner.",
